\v 10 Todavia, ainda que eles <a name="02800801000006" ll="SDBH:תנה:000000">merquem</a> socorros entre as <a name="02800801000012" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000">nações</a>, eu <a name="02800801000016" ll="SDBH:קבץ:000001">os</a> <a name="02800801000016" ll="SDBH:קבץ:000001">congregarei</a>; já <a name="02800801000020" ll="SDBH:חלל:001000" tl="HOTTP4143">começaram</a> a ser <a name="02800801000022" ll="SDBH:מְעַט:000001">diminuídos</a> por causa da <a name="02800801000026" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000005" tl="HOTTP4144">opressão</a> <a name="02800801000028" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">do</a> <a name="02800801000028" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> e dos <a name="02800801000030" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">príncipes</a>. 
\v 11 Porquanto <a name="02800801100006" ll="SDBH:אֶפְרַיִם:000001">Efraim</a> <a name="02800801100004">multiplicou</a> <a name="02800801100008" ll="SDBH:מִזְבֵּחַ:000000" il="HK00256;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c;Realia:4.2.1b;Realia:4.2.3">altares</a> para <a name="02800801100012" ll="SDBH:חטא:001005" tl="HOTTP4145">pecar</a>, <a name="02800801100018" ll="SDBH:מִזְבֵּחַ:000000" il="HK00256;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c;Realia:4.2.1b;Realia:4.2.3">estes</a> lhe foram para <a name="02800801100022" ll="SDBH:חטא:001005">pecar</a>. 
